OL,3,CDomestic abuse calls to police rise
OL,4,Cover festive period
OL,6,FThe number of domestic abuse`related
OL,7,Fcalls to the PSNI increased over the
OL,8,Ffestive period compared with the same
OL,9,Fperiod in 2024-25.
OL,11,F1,407 were made between 20 December
OL,12,Fand 2 January. The day with the most
OL,13,Fwas New Year's Day with 116, followed
OL,14,Fby Christmas Day with 115.
OL,16,FDuring the same period in 2024-25, the
OL,17,FPSNI received 1,290 calls.
OL,19,FThe newly-released figures for 2025-
OL,20,F2026 were the fourth-highest recorded
OL,21,Fin the last 10 years.
