OL,3,CDomestic abuse calls to police rise
OL,4,Cover festive period
OL,6,FDetective Superintendent Kerry Brennan
OL,7,Fsaid: "This time of year can place
OL,8,Fadditional pressures on households,
OL,9,Fincluding increased time spent
OL,10,Ftogether, financial strain, alcohol
OL,11,Fconsumption and heightened emotional
OL,12,Fstress.
OL,14,F"For some victims, these factors can
OL,15,Fescalate controlling or abusive
OL,16,Fbehaviour while for others the
OL,17,Fextended time at home can reduce
OL,18,Fopportunities to seek help or speak to
OL,19,Fsomeone in confidence.
